decision:
Update backend/kb/persistent.py to add workspace support:

1. Import Workspace and WorkspaceMode from .workspace and .schemas
2. In __init__ method, add: self.workspaces: Dict[str, Workspace] = {}
3. Add these methods after the existing ADR methods:

   def add_workspace(self, workspace: Workspace) -> None:
       '''Store or update a workspace'''
       self.workspaces[workspace.id] = workspace

   def get_workspace(self, workspace_id: str) -> Optional[Workspace]:
       '''Retrieve workspace by ID'''
       return self.workspaces.get(workspace_id)

   def list_workspaces(self) -> List[Workspace]:
       '''List all workspaces'''
       return list(self.workspaces.values())

   def remove_workspace(self, workspace_id: str) -> bool:
       '''Remove a workspace, returns True if existed'''
       if workspace_id in self.workspaces:
           del self.workspaces[workspace_id]
           return True
       return False

Follow the same pattern as add_adr, get_adr methods.

